snippet.title: Hyper DBZ - 3 / 5.0 - Eighteen Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready for our first female hyper fighter! Yes we know, it's taking a while! But I'd just like to remind you that we all have jobs and this is just a cool hobby for us! With a lot of progress done on Eighteen, we're inching further forward towards the release of our biggest and baddest build, the fifth one.

Shoutouts to the main devs working on her: XGargoyle (coding) and NicotineFist (sprites). She's currently in the lab with our testers hard at work (shoutouts to them too!) She'll come out a champ!

Yeah that's right, we got the lovely Danielle McRae to voice Eighteen, what's up? https://twitter.com/DanielleMcVO  https://www.imdb.com/name/nm3683843/

Eighteen's funky fresh theme by DaMarcus008. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hB2b9oEjntY

If you read this far, good on you! You deserve a smooch from Eighteen! X
